sc_635_world folder in home directory
run_sc635_sim.sh in home also

follow catkin workspace creation (step 3 on http://wiki.ros.org/ROS/Tutorials/InstallingandConfiguringROSEnvironment) assuming ROS is installed

after doing catkin_make
paste the package folder sbot_controller in the home/catkin_ws/src folder


to run stuff run the commands in a terminal:
$ cd ~/ 
$ sudo ./run_sc635_sim.sh 

in a new terminal window
to run the controller node, run the following:

$ cd ~/catkin_ws
$ source devel/setup.bash
$ rosrun sbot_controller controller.py

